---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Workshops | Arkadi Avanesyan" description="Free live workshops on portfolio management and quantitative finance.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-6 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-full mb-4">
        Free Live Workshop
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        Build Your First <span class="gradient-text">Crisis-Proof Portfolio</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-2">
        Learn the framework I developed over 10 years at Goldman Sachs and Societe Generale.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-500">
        Thursday, March 12, 2026 — 7:00 PM UTC — 45 minutes
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-6 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
        <!-- Left: Details -->
        <div class="lg:w-2/3">
          <!-- The Problem -->
          <div class="card mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Problem</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
              When markets crashed in 2022, many tech professionals watched <strong>30-40% of their savings evaporate</strong>. Not because of bad luck or poor stock picks — but because their portfolios were structurally designed to fail in a crisis.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
              Most portfolios are optimized for growth. They perform beautifully in bull markets. They fall apart when it matters most.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- What You'll Learn -->
          <div class="card mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What You'll Learn</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Antifragility Concept</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Identify investments that actually strengthen during volatility — not just survive it.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Three-Category Classification</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Learn to classify every position as Fragile, Robust, or Antifragile.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Structural Flaws</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Understand why traditional portfolios cause panic-selling — and how to avoid it.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">The Key Question</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">"Does this asset benefit from volatility — or just survive it?" This changes everything.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Who This Is For -->
          <div class="card mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Who This Is For</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600">
              Tech professionals and individual investors seeking to build resilient portfolios using institutional-grade frameworks adapted for personal use. No prior quantitative finance experience required.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- About the Instructor -->
          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">About the Instructor</h2>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <img
                src="/Arkadi.A.jpg"
                alt="Arkadi Avanesyan"
                class="w-20 h-20 rounded-xl object-cover flex-shrink-0"
              />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Arkadi Avanesyan</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-1">
                  Quant Developer based in Luxembourg with 10+ years building institutional investment products. Work commercialized by Societe Generale across 60+ countries. Used by Goldman Sachs and Deutsche Bank in €1.5B+ structured products.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-2">
                  Teaching 80,000+ students on Coursera, Udemy, and Codementor.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Registration Card -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/3">
          <div class="card bg-slate-900 text-white border-0 sticky top-24">
            <img
              src="/Arkadi.L1.png"
              alt="Workshop Preview"
              class="w-full rounded-xl mb-6"
            />
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Thursday, March 12, 2026</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">7:00 PM UTC · 45 minutes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Live on Zoom + Q&A</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">Free</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://maven.com/p/62cecb/build-your-first-crisis-proof-portfolio"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="block w-full text-center bg-white text-slate-900 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors"
            >
              Register Free
            </a>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs text-center mt-4">
              Hosted on Maven
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
